# Data Retention Policy

_Generated by SKILL-NEXTJS (W6 #280). Replace placeholder text before shipping._

## Scope

This policy covers all personal data processed by **{{ project_name }}**.

## Retention periods

| Category              | Retention | Legal basis                 |
|-----------------------|-----------|-----------------------------|
| Account profile       | Until account deletion + 30 days | Contract (GDPR Art. 6(1)(b)) |
| Authentication logs   | 180 days  | Legitimate interest (fraud) |
| Transactional records | 7 years   | Tax / accounting law        |
| Marketing consent log | Until withdrawal + 3 years | Consent (GDPR Art. 6(1)(a)) |

## Right to erasure

Users may request erasure via `POST /api/v1/privacy/erasure`. The
backend processes within 30 days (GDPR Art. 17). Sub-processors are
notified through the same request.

## Data Processing Agreement

A DPA template is available on request; see `docs/privacy/dpa.md`.
